entries.title: Twitter Hasn't Paid Bill, M&A Advisory Firm Says
entries.description: Innisfree M&A sues Twitter for $1.9 million, saying it hasn’t been paid for services in the months leading up to Elon Musk’s acquisition of the social-media platform.

entries.title: Tesla Nudges Up Model Y Prices
entries.description: Tesla has raised prices in the U.S. for its Model Y SUV.

entries.title: Don't Be the Parent Who Ghostwrites the Kids' Texts
entries.description: Composing texts for your teens doesn’t teach them communication skills. Convey this advice from etiquette experts instead.

entries.title: AI Tech Enables Industrial-Scale Intellectual-Property Theft, Say Critics
entries.description: Are ChatGPT, Stability AI and GitHub Copilot the next big breakthroughs, huge legal and regulatory liabilities, or something else entirely?
